data.description: Experience refined living in this impeccably maintained Sitterle Homes masterpiece. This single-story 4 bed/3 bath home, complete with a home office and 3-car garage, graces a greenbelt lot and offers stunning hill country views. The well-appointed kitchen, boasting double ovens and a spacious island, seamlessly connects to the dining and family room areas with panoramic Boerne hill country views. The master suite impresses with double vanities, an expansive twin shower, and a large walk-in closet. Additional bedrooms and a dedicated home office provide ample space for any lifestyle. Relish the tranquility of nature from the spacious covered back patio, perfect for relaxation. This home harmonizes meticulous craftsmanship with hill country beauty. Don't miss this chance to experience luxury living at its finest. Schedule your private tour today and capture the essence of Boerne's hill country charm.
